            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Commonitorium deo <lb n="2"/>Mercurio <del rend="erasure">Marti Silvano</del> a Satur<lb break="no" n="3"/>nina muliere de lintia<lb break="no" n="4"/>mine quod amisit ut il<lb break="no" n="5"/>le qui ho<supplied reason="lost">c</supplied> circumvenit non <lb n="6"/>ante laxetur nissi <note>sic</note> quand<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="7"/>res s<expan><ex>upra</ex><abbr>dictas</abbr></expan> ad fanum s<expan><ex>upra</ex><abbr>d</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">ic</supplied><lb break="no" n="8"/>tum attul<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>rit si vir si mu<lb break="no" n="9"/>lier si servus s<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> liber </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> deo s<expan><ex>upra</ex><abbr>dicto</abbr></expan> tertiam <lb n="2"/>partem donat ita ut <lb n="3"/>exsigat <note>sic</note> istas res quae s<expan><ex>upra</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>crip</ex><abbr>ta</abbr></expan> sunt <lb n="4"/>ACA quae <note>sic</note> per<expan><ex>didi</ex><abbr>t</abbr></expan> deo Silvano <lb n="5"/>tertia pars donatur ita ut <lb n="6"/>hoc exsigat <note>sic</note> si vir si femina si s<supplied reason="lost">erv</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>us si liber <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>at
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gebet für Gerechtigkeit. (B): Abweichende Textgestaltung.</p>
            </div>
